cast iron</link> pan more than a meter in diameter, the socca is seasoned generously with <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../116/150116.xml">
black pepper</link> and eaten  while hot with the fingers.  Socca is considered by some to be a chickpea <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../355/333355.xml">
crepe</link>, as the preparation and consistency of the batter is similar.
